'''Leo Bagrow''' (1881 [[Saint Petersburg]]{{sfn|Harley|Woodward|1987|p=26}} – 9 August 1957 [[The Hague]]),{{sfn|Skelton|1959|p=5}} born '''Lev Solomonovich Bagrow''',{{sfn|Harley|Woodward|1987|p=26}} was a historian of cartography and the founder of the journal ''[[Imago Mundi]]''.

