{|class="wikitable" |- ! width="110"|Flag!!width="100"|Date!!width="250"|Use!!width="250"|Description!!width="350"|Usage |- | [[File:Flag of Thailand.svg|150px]] || 2017–present || Flag of Thailand || Five horizontal stripes of red, white, blue, white and red, the middle stripe twice as wide as the others. || National flag |}
==Royal flags==
===Royal standards=== {| class="wikitable" |- ! width="110"|Flag!!width="100"|Date!!width="250"|Use!!width="250"|Description |- | [[File:King's Standard of Thailand.svg|100px|border]] || 1911– || [[Royal Standard of Thailand|Royal Standard]] of the [[King of Thailand]] ||A yellow plain square flag with a dancing red [[emblem of Thailand|Garuda]] in the center. Usually mounted in front of the car boarded by the King. |- | [[File:Queen's Standard of Thailand.svg|130px|border]] || 1911– || Standard of the [[List of Thai royal consorts|Queen of Thailand]] || King's Standard in ratio 2:3 with swallow-tailed end. |- | [[File:Boromrajawong Yai Flag of Thailand.svg|130px|border]] || 1979– || Standard for Senior members of the Royal Family (created for the [[Srinagarindra|Princess Mother]]) || Queen's Standard in ratio 2:3 with swallow-tailed end. The blue middle square depicts the Royal Crown atop two bowls on a table flanked by two five-tiered royal umbrellas. |- | [[File:Crown Prince's Standard of Thailand.svg|100px|border]] || 1911– || Standard of the [[Crown Prince of Thailand]]. ||Thai king's standard with blue border. |- | [[File:Consort of Crown Prince's Standard of Thailand.svg|130px|border]] || 1911– || Standard for the Royal Consort of the Crown Prince of Thailand. ||Blue 2:3 rectangle defaced with King's Standard. The flag is swallow-tailed. |- | [[File:Male Royalty's Standard of Thailand.svg|100px|border]] || 1911– || Standard for other princes in the [[Chakri Dynasty]]. ||Blue square defaced with yellow circle. The circle features red Garuda. |- | [[File:Female Royalty's Standard of Thailand.svg|130px|border]] || 1911– || Standard for other princesses in the Chakri Dynasty. ||Standard for the male royalties in ratio 2:3 with swallow-tailed end. |- | [[File:Standard of the Regent of Thailand.svg|100px|border]] || 1936– || Standard for the [[Chakri Dynasty#Regents|Regent of Thailand]]. || A white plain square flag with the Garuda and a shield depicting the National Flag in the center. |}
===Personal royal flags=== {| class="wikitable" |- ! width="110"|Flag!!width="100"|Date!!width="250"|Use!!width="250"|Description |- | [[File:Royal Flag of King Rama X.svg|150px|border]] || 2016–present || [[Royal Flags of Thailand|Personal Flag of]] [[Vajiralongkorn|HM King Vajiralongkorn]] || Yellow flag (the King's [[Color of the day|birthday colour]]), the middle the depicts the [[Royal Cypher]] ('''ว.ป.ร.''': มหา'''ว'''ชิราลงกรณ '''ป'''รม'''ร'''าชาธิราช : Maha'''v'''ajiralongkorn '''P'''arama'''r'''ajadhirajatiraj (Thai equivalent to Vajiralongkorn Rex), topped by the [[Great Crown of Victory]], in between is the Thai numeral of 10. |- | [[File:Royal Flag of Queen Sirikit.svg|150px|border]] || 1950–present || [[Royal Flags of Thailand|Personal Flag of]] [[Sirikit|HM Queen Mother Sirikit]] || Blue flag (the Queen's [[Color of the day|birthday colour]]), the middle the depicts the [[Royal Cypher]] ('''ส.ก.''': '''สิ'''ริ'''กิ'''ติ์ : '''S'''iri'''k'''it), the middle is Queen Sirikit's Royal Cypher, topped by the Great Crown of Victory. |- | [[File:Royal Flag of Princess Maha Chakri Sirindhorn.svg|150px|border]] || 1977–present || [[Royal Flags of Thailand|Personal Flag of]] [[Sirindhorn|HRH Princess Maha Chakri Sirindhorn]] || Purple flag (the Princess’ [[Color of the day|birthday colour]]), the middle the depicts the [[Royal Cypher]] ('''ส.ธ.''': '''สิ'''ริน'''ธ'''ร : '''S'''irin'''d'''horn), the middle is the Royal Cypher, topped by the simplified crown. |- | [[File:Royal Flag of Princess Chulabhorn Walailak.svg|150px|border]] || 1982–present || [[Royal Flags of Thailand|Personal Flag of]] [[Chulabhorn|HRH Princess Chulabhorn Walailak]] || Orange flag (the Princess’ [[Color of the day|birthday colour]]), the middle the depicts the [[Royal Cypher]] ('''จ.ภ.''': '''จุ'''ฬา'''ภ'''รณวลัยลักษณ์ : '''C'''hula'''b'''horn), the middle is the Royal Cypher, topped by the simplified crown. |- | [[File:Royal Flag of Princess Ubolratana Rajakanya.svg|150px|border]] || 2001–present || [[Royal Flags of Thailand|Personal Flag of]] [[Ubol Ratana|Princess Ubolratana Rajakanya]] || Red flag (the Princess’ [[Color of the day|birthday colour]]), the middle the depicts the [[Royal Cypher]] ('''อ.ร.''': '''อุ'''บล'''รั'''ตนราชกัญญา : '''U'''bol'''r'''atana), the middle is the Royal Cypher, but not topped by the simplified crown. |- | [[File:Royal Flag of Princess Soamsavali.svg|150px|border]] || 1977–present || [[Royal Flags of Thailand|Personal Flag of]] [[Soamsawali|HRH Princess Soamsawali]] || Purple flag (the Princess’ [[Color of the day|birthday colour]]), the middle the depicts the [[Royal Cypher]] ('''ส.ส.''': โ'''ส'''ม'''ส'''วลี : '''S'''oam'''s'''awali), the middle is the Royal Cypher, under the Buddhist/Hindu sacred sign of "Unalome". |- | [[File:Royal Flag of Princess Bajrakitiyabha.svg|150px|border]] || 1978–present || [[Royal Flags of Thailand|Personal Flag of]] [[Bajrakitiyabha|HRH Princess Bajrakitiyabha]] || Orange flag (the Princess’ [[Color of the day|birthday colour]]), the middle the depicts the [[Royal Cypher]] ('''พ.ภ.''': '''พั'''ชรกิติยา'''ภ'''า : '''B'''ajrakitiya'''b'''ha), the middle is the Royal Cypher. |- | [[File:Royal Flag of Princess Sirivannavari Nariratana.svg|150px|border]] || 2005–present || [[Royal Flags of Thailand|Personal Flag of]] [[Sirivannavari Nariratana|HRH Princess Sirivannavari Nariratana]] || Orange flag (the Princess’ [[Color of the day|birthday colour]]), the middle the depicts the [[Royal Cypher]] ('''ส.ร.''': '''สิ'''ริวัณณว'''รี'''นารีรัตน์ : '''S'''irivannava'''r'''i), the middle is the Royal Cypher. |- | [[File:Royal Flag of Prince Dipangkorn Rasmijoti.svg|150px|border]] || 2005–present || [[Royal Flags of Thailand|Personal Flag of]] [[Dipangkorn Rasmijoti|HRH Prince Dipangkorn Rasmijoti]] || Blue flag (the Prince’s [[Color of the day|birthday colour]]), the middle the depicts the [[Royal Cypher]] ('''ท.ป.''': '''ทีปั'''งกรรัศมีโชติ : '''D'''i'''p'''angkorn), the middle is the Royal Cypher. |- | [[File:Royal Flag of Princess Siribhachudhabhorn.svg|150px|border]] || 1982–present || [[Royal Flags of Thailand|Personal Flag of]] [[Siribhachudabhorn|HRH Princess Siribhachudabhorn]] || Blue flag (the Princess’ [[Color of the day|birthday colour]]), the middle the depicts the [[Royal Cypher]] ('''ส.ภ.''': '''สิ'''ริ'''ภ'''าจุฑาภรณ์ : '''S'''iri'''b'''hachudabhorn), the middle is the Royal Cypher. |- | [[File:Royal Flag of Princess Aditayadornkitikhun.svg|150px|border]] || 2016–present || [[Royal Flags of Thailand|Personal Flag of]] [[Aditayadornkitikhun|HRH Princess Aditayadornkitikhun]] || Purple flag (the Princess’ [[Color of the day|birthday colour]]), the middle the depicts the [[Royal Cypher]] ('''อ.ก.''': '''อ'''ทิตยาทร'''กิ'''ติคุณ : '''A'''ditayadorn'''k'''itikhun), the middle is the Royal Cypher. |}
== Royal Thai Government flags == {| class="wikitable" |- ! width="110"|Flag!!width="100"|Date!!width="250"|Use!!width="250"|Description |- |[[File:Flag of the Prime Minister of Thailand.svg|130px|border]] || 1979– || Flag of the [[Prime Minister of Thailand]] || White flag in ratio 5:6 with the Prime Minister's seal under the royal crown. |- |[[File:Flag of the Thai Defence Minister.svg|130px|border]] || 1936– || Flag of the [[Ministry of Defence (Thailand)|Minister of Defence of Thailand]] || White flag in ratio 5:6 with the Emblem of the Ministry of Defence in the center. The emblem consists of a red chakra (Army), the dark blue anchor (Navy) and the sky blue wings (Air Force). |- |[[File:Flag of the President of the National Assembly of Thailand.svg|130px|border]] || 1979– || Flag of the [[President of the National Assembly of Thailand]] || White flag in ratio 5:6 with the National Assembly of Thailand's seal under the royal crown. |- |[[File:Flag of the President of the Supreme Court of Thailand.svg|130px|border]] || 1979– || Flag of the President of the [[Supreme Court of Thailand]] || White flag in ratio 5:6 with the Supreme Court of Thailand's seal under the royal crown. |}
== Naval flags ==
{| class="wikitable" |- ! width="110"|Flag!!width="100"|Date!!width="250"|Use!!width="250"|Description |- | [[File:Thailand Naval Jack (Thong Chan).svg|150px]] || 1917– || Naval [[Jack (flag)|Jack]] || A national flag with the emblem of [[Royal Thai Navy]] in the center: a chakra inserted with an anchor under the Thai royal crown. The design is identical to Thai naval unit colours. Note that all Thai Army, Navy and Air Force unit colours called "''[[Colours, standards and guidons#Thailand|Thong Chai Chalermphol]]''{{-"}} ([[:th:ธงชัยเฉลิมพล|ธงชัยเฉลิมพล]]). |- | [[File:Naval Ensign of Thailand.svg|150px]] || 1917– || [[Naval Ensign]] || A red disc containing a white elephant in regalia centred on the national flag. |}
== Military flags == {| class="wikitable" |- ! width="110"|Flag!!width="100"|Date!!width="250"|Use!!width="250"|Description |- |[[File:Royal Thai Army Flag.svg|150px]] || 1979– || [[Royal Thai Army]] Flag || Red flag with the emblem of [[Royal Thai Army]]: a chakra under Unalom and the Thai royal crown with rays flanked by the wreaths (from Flag law B.E.2522 (1979)). |- | [[File:Royal Thai Navy Flag.svg|150px]] || 1979– || [[Royal Thai Navy]] Flag || Navy blue flag with the emblem of [[Royal Thai Navy]] in the white circle (from Flag law B.E.2522 (1979)). |- | [[File:Royal Thai Air Force Flag.svg|150px]] || 1979– || [[Royal Thai Air Force]] Flag || Blue sky flag with the emblem of [[Royal Thai Air Force]]: wings with Unalom under the Thai royal crown and rays (from Flag law B.E.2522 (1979)). |- | [[File:Flag for Commander-in-Chief of the Royal Thai Army.svg|150px]]|| 1979– || Flag for [[List of Commanders of the Royal Thai Army|Commander-in-Chief of the Royal Thai Army]] || Red flag with the emblem of [[Royal Thai Army]] with five stars underneath. |- | [[File:Flag for Commander-in-Chief of the Royal Thai Navy.svg|150px]]|| 1897– || Flag for [[List of Commanders of the Royal Thai Navy|Commander-in-Chief of the Royal Thai Navy]] || Navy blue flag with the emblem of [[Royal Thai Navy]]. |- | [[File:Flag for Commander-in-Chief of the Royal Thai Air Force.svg|150px]]|| 1979– || Flag for [[List of Commanders of the Royal Thai Air Force|Commander-in-Chief of the Royal Thai Air Force]] || Blue sky flag with yellow borders and the emblem of [[Royal Thai Air Force]] with a shield depicting the National flag. |}
== Police flag == {| class="wikitable" |- ! width="110"|Flag!!width="100"|Date!!width="250"|Use!!width="250"|Description |- |[[File:Thai National Police Flag.svg|150px]] || 1958– || [[Royal Thai Police|Royal Thai Police Headquarters]] || Maroon red flag with the emblem of the Thai National Police in the center. |- |[[File:Phithaksantirat flag of the Royal Thai Police.svg|150px]] || 1979– || Pitak Santiraj flag || An honour flag of the Royal Thai Police according to the Thai Flag Act of B.E. 2522 (1979). It has the same characteristics and colors as the National Flag but in the centre of the flag is the coat of arms of Siam during the reign of King Chulalongkorn (Rama V), with the words “To Protect the People’s Peace” (พิทักษ์สันติราษฎร์ - pronounce ''"Pitak Santiraj"'') embroidered in silver metallic threads embracing the underside of the coat of arms. |}
== Religious flags == {| class="wikitable" |- ! width="110"|Flag!!width="100"|Date!!width="250"|Use!!width="250"|Description |- |[[File:Dharmacakra flag (Thailand).svg|150px]] || 1958– || The [[Dharmacakra]] flag—Buddhism || Yellow is color of Buddhism, the middle the depicts the Red Thammachak, symbol of The Buddhism Organizations and Buddhists in Thailand. |}
== Diplomatic flags == {| class="wikitable" |- ! width="110"|Flag!!width="100"|Date!!width="250"|Use!!width="250"|Description |- | [[File:Ambassador flag of Thailand.svg|150px]] || 1927– || Ambassador Standard of Thailand || A blue disc containing a [[white elephant (animal)|white elephant]] in regalia centred on the national flag. |- | [[File:Consular flag of Thailand.svg|150px]] || 1927– || Consular Flag of Thailand || Triranga surmounted with blue disc containing a white elephant. |}
