id_Bernier_in_2014_.jpg|150px|David Bernier]] {{!}} [[David Bernier]] {{!}} [[Puerto Rican general election, 2016|2016]] {{!}} lost {{!}} * 23rd [[Secretary of State of Puerto Rico]] * former President of the [[Puerto Rico Olympic Committee]] }} |}
