{{Orphan|date=March 2017}}

The '''Madonna Falls''', is a [[waterfall]] believed to hold [[mana]] and have healing properties. The waterfall is located close to [[New Zealand State Highway 4|State Highway 4]] about {{convert|14|km}} from the town of [[Mapiu]].<ref>http://www.teara.govt.nz/TheBush/Landscapes/Waterfalls/4/ENZ-Resources/Standard/4/en</ref>

{{coord|38|29|58.74|S|175|11|26.65|E|region:NZ|display=inline,title}}

